name: SICGEAR BARCODE LOGO TEE
description: It may be the first, the unknown, the unaccepted but one day soon it will be a force to be reckoned with. We will be forming an army, and all are welcomed to join. Here is your first option for a uniform, a badge of honor, a symbol stating that we will no longer be "PRODUCTS" of society, and in stead be a product of ourselves. One and all under one banner, that banner being SICGEAR.
